{"tid":2455902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本最美童星17歲了！近照曝光網民傻眼：同一人？","createTime":"2021-03-21T13:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T05:40:37.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"377e182799f3a9553810e1dcd381a9d1de9aba84","tid":2455902,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"四方報報導，所謂小時了了大未必佳，放眼海內外演藝圈，童星長大後外型不如從前可愛的例子數不勝數，不少前途被看好的童星也隨著年紀增長退去光芒。其中，曾號稱「日本最美童星」的谷花音（Kanon Tani）就是一個例子，不少粉絲在看到她的近照後都直呼與小時候的記憶相去甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2021/03/1616144054107-4eb4770e5e284266a101ae0c2c88a4d0-800x480.png?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2021%2F03%2F1616144054107-4eb4770e5e284266a101ae0c2c88a4d0-800x480.png%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=57dffc8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n谷花音2004年出生於日本，從小就長得十分可愛她，憑著精緻又帶有混血感的臉蛋，在3歲就成為兒童模特兒，更在5歲踏入演藝圈開始拍戲，獲封「日本最美童星」。谷花音不僅外型精緻，還擁有一秒落淚的神級演技，不少和他共同拍過戲的人都表示，她在片場很少NG，頗有演戲天份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2021/03/1616144239477-687e95a7966a4f88952e580ecb171845-800x480.png?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2021%2F03%2F1616144239477-687e95a7966a4f88952e580ecb171845-800x480.png%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=53b15713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2021/03/1616144053924-56013f033d2a49119622fd5f5529e1ae-800x480.png?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2021%2F03%2F1616144053924-56013f033d2a49119622fd5f5529e1ae-800x480.png%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=c37c4248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲曾號稱「日本最美童星」谷花音（Kanon Tani）近照曝光。<br />\n<br />\n一轉眼，已經經過17個年頭，谷花音也從童星長成一名青春少女。然而，曾經前途一片看好的她如今卻聲勢大跌，加上美國債息持續高企，以及受累國際油價急挫，不若從前般擁有高人氣。不少網友在看到谷花音的近照後都表示，成年之後的她與年幼時的精緻臉蛋相去甚遠，幾乎認不出是同一人。現在仍是高校生的谷花音在美國留學中，憑藉著幼年時累積起來的出色演技，還是在近年推出不少好作品如《請不要在病房裡念佛》，獲得影迷肯定。"},{"pid":"7feed855e88a8b87370d94d121b912e6687d879d","tid":2455902,"uid":6842,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"加上美國債息持續高企，以及受累國際油價急挫<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04073177908ac88e7a0629817c0b845968062df0","tid":2455902,"uid":102356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"千雪"},{"pid":"d09e7642d9656baa8813d1cea97da65152ba6e69","tid":2455902,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得五觀ok 係塊形出事<br />\n而且日本妹話變就變<br />\n暫時未到好樣衰既地步"},{"pid":"1816b738f397da17db7eeed8b424f8fdfbf90260","tid":2455902,"uid":9183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"然而，曾經前途一片看好的她如今卻聲勢大跌，加上美國債息持續高企，以及受累國際油價急挫，不若從前般擁有高人氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c001585f273257583efc60922a48244f3f035e36","tid":2455902,"uid":171192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1816b738f397da17db7eeed8b424f8fdfbf90260","tid":2455902,"uid":9183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"然而，曾經前途一片看好的她如今卻聲勢大跌，加上美國債息持續高企，以及受累國際油價急挫，不若從前般擁有高人氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696a53b9bad95aa3fbb6645085c4212601cba959","tid":2455902,"uid":57570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-